)
Σ
 

X

i


=
0


{\displaystyle \Sigma \ X_{i}Y_{i}={\hat {b}}\Sigma \ {X_{i}}^{2}+({\bar {Y}}-{\hat {b}}{\bar {X}})\Sigma \ X_{i}=0}



