{\displaystyle {\hat {b}}={\frac {\Sigma \ X_{i}Y_{i}-{\bar {Y}}\Sigma \ X_{i}}{\Sigma \ {X_{i}}^{2}-{\bar {X}}\Sigma \ X_{i}}}}









a
